Warblender Installation
=======================


In UN*X, type:

make install

You can also specify the target install directory with the BLENDERSCRIPTSDIR
variable (defaults to ~/.blender/scripts/).


In Windows, copy the following:

warblender/
warblender_import.py
warblender_export.py

to %BLENDERDIR%/.blender/scripts/

%BLENDERDIR% is usually C:\Program Files\Blender Foundation\Blender.
